</sp>
<sp><speaker>TERESA</speaker><l> Solo? </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>NERI</speaker><l> Tu crepi! ci vorrà anco l'ago. </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>TERESA</speaker><l> A voi, vi pigli 'r canchero. </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>NERI</speaker><l> O 'r cotone? </l>
</sp>
