</sp>
<sp><speaker>CLEMENTINA</speaker><l> Chi è? </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>LODOVICO</speaker><l> Apri, son' io. </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>CLEMENTINA</speaker><l> O la rivista?… Velgine beata! </l>
<l>Come siei mézzo, pover' amol mio! </l>
<l>Stella. </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>STELLA</speaker><l> Comandi! </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>CLEMENTINA</speaker><l> Fate 'na fiammata… </l>
<l>Lo dicevo: vòr piove', Dolovìo… </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>LODOVICO</speaker><l> Brrr. .. </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>CLEMENTINA</speaker><l> Ti fa freddo? </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>LODOVICO</speaker><l> Eh, sfido, a quest'acquata </l>
<l>Ma la Nazione… </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>CLEMENTINA</speaker><l> Spògliati, ti dio!… </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>LODOVICO</speaker><l> Parlerà… </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>CLEMENTINA</speaker><l> Malidetto la parata! </l>
<l>Stella. </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>STELLA</speaker><l> <pb n="889"/>
Ho già fatto: vienghin' a scardassi, </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>LODOVICO</speaker><l> … Der valore… </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>CLEMENTINA</speaker><l> Dirre' quarch'eresia. </l>
<l>Sentite che camicia! è da strizzassi. </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>LODOVICO</speaker><l> Quanto freddo ho patito, anima mia! </l>
<l>Brrr… ma la grolia 'nsenza strapazzassi… </l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>STELLA</speaker><l> Sol padrone, si spenge; vienga via. </l>
</sp><trailer><hi rend="italic">Firenze</hi>, <num>1871</num></trailer>
